    { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest-scoring Scrabble words starting with ANTI-?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "ANTIQUELY (21 pts), ANTIQUES (17 pts), and ANTICKING (16 pts) rank among the top ANTI- words. The prefix adds 4 base points (A1+N1+T1+I1) to any root." }},
