<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Words Starting With ANTI- — Scrabble Prefix Scoring Guide</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The ANTI- prefix means "against" or "opposite" and is one of Scrabble's most versatile word-starters. With over 200 valid ANTI- words in SOWPODS, this prefix lets you extend existing plays, build bingos from common roots, and rack up serious points through high-value combinations like ANTIQUE and ANTIQUELY.</p>

<p>Mastering ANTI- words gives you both offensive firepower and defensive flexibility, especially when opponents leave exploitable openings on the board.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why ANTI- Matters in Scrabble</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">A(1)+N(1)+T(1)+I(1) base</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">200+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid ANTI- words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4–15</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>Because ANTI- uses only common, low-value tiles, it's easy to hold these letters without sacrificing rack flexibility. The real power comes from what you attach after the prefix — high-value roots containing Q, X, K, or Z tiles.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring ANTI- Words</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
  <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
